WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Stop guessing what makes a YouTube video go viral.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:07.500
Most creators rely on recycled advice and gut feelings.

00:00:07.500 --> 00:00:11.000
But what if you could let hard data drive your content strategy?

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:13.000
Welcome to Creator Luck.

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:17.000
Creator Luck allows you to instantly uncover
the top-performing content in any niche.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:21.000
Simply type in your topic, and our platform
pulls in the most relevant videos.

00:00:21.000 --> 00:00:25.500
You can easily filter by long-form content,
YouTube Shorts, and specific timeframes

00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:31.000
to ensure you're analyzing what's working right now.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:35.000
But here is where the magic happens.
Select a batch of videos and hit Analyze.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:39.000
Creator Luck doesn't just look at views —

00:00:39.000 --> 00:00:43.000
